{"id":287258,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/维权网-上海公民赵渊经营20余年的餐厅面临无补偿/","date":"2013-04-02T10:32:14Z","modified":"2013-04-02T10:32:14Z","title":"维权网 | 上海公民赵渊经营20余年的餐厅面临无补偿强拆（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员郑广源报道）上海华敏餐厅合法经营者赵渊夫妇，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1988</span><span>年通过合法手续，向上海市徐汇区华泾镇龙华村村委会申请批地，经村委同意，在该村边角地自建有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>㎡的华敏餐厅经营房屋。经工商、税务、卫生等相关部门批准的合法经营餐饮业达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>年之久。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>徐汇区政府《沪徐府土（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>号》规范性文件，将华敏餐厅列入拆迁范围。业主赵渊表态“在本人利益得到保障的前提下予以全力配合”。但拆迁人至今未有拆迁补偿安置的具体措施，令人费解。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>期间，官商勾结将赵渊经营了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多年的华敏餐厅房地产权利登记在上海天钥实业有限公司名下，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年上海天钥实业有限公司莫名其妙地向徐汇区法院起诉，以建造“集散中心”名义，要求赵渊与非产权人的徐丽敏“返还华敏餐厅占有物”，徐汇法院将赵渊的华敏餐厅经营房变成了“天钥公司”的产权。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>目前，该地块经营性项目“商务楼”在建造过程中，该地块显然不是什么“公共利益”的拆迁，行政不宜干预。然而，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>，徐汇区法院《公告》居然将赵渊使用了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>年之久的华敏餐厅，变称为了“临时搭建物”要求返还“占有物”并责令赵渊与前妻在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年前无补偿搬离，“返还”给无关联的“天钥公司”，让“天钥公司”无本获利！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>敬请各界爱好和平、争取民主自由、推动社会进步的人们密切关注在习近平、李克强新一届领导下的上海动用司法强拆的自由和他的华敏餐厅的命运！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>联系赵渊：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13636590576       </span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-UoPHlxL_H-E/UVql0KMaN0I/AAAAAAAAfr8/3z7-iktuPPg/s1600/1+2013%E5%B9%B43%E6%9C%8825%E6%97%A5%E5%BE%90%E6%B1%87%E5%8C%BA%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E3%80%8A%E5%85%AC%E5%91%8A%E3%80%8B%E8%A6%81%E5%AF%B9%E8%B5%B5%E6%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%8E%E6%95%8F%E9%A4%90%E5%8E%85%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%BC%BA%E6%8B%86.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-UoPHlxL_H-E/UVql0KMaN0I/AAAAAAAAfr8/3z7-iktuPPg/s320/1+2013%E5%B9%B43%E6%9C%8825%E6%97%A5%E5%BE%90%E6%B1%87%E5%8C%BA%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E3%80%8A%E5%85%AC%E5%91%8A%E3%80%8B%E8%A6%81%E5%AF%B9%E8%B5%B5%E6%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%8E%E6%95%8F%E9%A4%90%E5%8E%85%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%BC%BA%E6%8B%86.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-zqWtjIOomxs/UVql4dE8kXI/AAAAAAAAfsI/pt_6xRRpDis/s1600/2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2599%25A2+%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25AE%259A%25E4%25B9%25A6.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"236\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-zqWtjIOomxs/UVql4dE8kXI/AAAAAAAAfsI/pt_6xRRpDis/s320/2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2599%25A2+%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25AE%259A%25E4%25B9%25A6.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}